### 创建素材
POST {{host}}/v1/material_library
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "title": "测试素材标题",
  "content": "这是测试素材的内容\n\n**支持Markdown格式**",
  "tags": ["测试", "示例"]
}

### 获取素材详情（包含content）
GET {{host}}/v1/material_library/1
Authorization: {{token}}

### 更新素材
PUT {{host}}/v1/material_library/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "title": "更新后的素材标题",
  "content": "这是更新后的素材内容\n\n增加了新的内容",
  "tags": ["测试", "更新"]
}
### 分页查询素材列表（不包含content）
GET {{host}}/v1/material_library?page=1&page_size=10&title=&tag=
Authorization: {{token}}

### 删除素材
DELETE {{host}}/v1/material_library/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}